{"tid":2047000,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"同大家講吓美國示威究竟為乜同示威者去 Target 偷野又為乜","createTime":"2020-06-01T20:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T22:01:46.000Z","uid":301795,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe3f3c574f5c8532067e41d7f69feffe6d0c46b","tid":2047000,"uid":301795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T20:54:56.000Z","msg":"啱啱開會同一堆美國同事討論緊香港同美國近況，會議後一個黑人同事 send 咗條 link 講點解死一個人會爆到咁大，或者大家做 twitter 任割 looters 前可以了解吓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4amCfVbA_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv4amCfVbA_c&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=17e57bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4amCfVbA_c</a><br />\n<br />\n條片有啲長，而且用英文，我講少少重點&hellip;<br />\n爆到咁大唔係因為死一個人，而係黑人一直都係二等公民，受到各種差別待遇。<br />\n例子一<br />\nAmy Cooper<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iUQWd4q3tjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiUQWd4q3tjA&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=d44f3be1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iUQWd4q3tjA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ceFK5S7ACs4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DceFK5S7ACs4&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=5825a9ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ceFK5S7ACs4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子二<br />\nAhmaud Arbery <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tt5XbmPqJQM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dtt5XbmPqJQM&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbXaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=12dc1bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tt5XbmPqJQM</a> <br />\n<br />\n上面兩個係近期比較多人知嘅例子，但係無上報嘅事例非黑人嘅你又知幾多？設身啲諗就好似香港示威者成日俾狗跪頸俾狗咬仲有各種各樣言語肢體性暴力，報紙會報嘅同你知道嘅同你唔知道嘅係咩比例我地大家心裡面大概都有個數字。George Floyd 一事就好似有個手足喺你面前俾狗咬死咗咁。咁講大家會唔會更加感受到？<br />\n<br />\n另一個片裡面重點講點解要去 loot Target。應該話點解唔去 loot Target。偷野唔啱？犯法？Target 無辜唔應該搞佢？片裡面講法係，點解唔啱點解犯法點解無辜就唔應該搞其實都係因為一個 social contract。簡單講，喺一個文明社會上我選擇去守某些規則以換取我以外嘅人去守某些規則，尼個係我同社會嘅一個合約，一個我一踏入被會就被逼簽嘅 agreement。而加對黑人黎講，其實社會一直無律守社會一方嘅合約條款，咁點解佢地要再同你守個合約去唔偷野唔犯法唔搞無辜嘅 Target？尼個講調未必說服到你，但係或者你會更加明白 Why loot Target 背後個 Why not。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，同事話宣報咗 23:00 後宵禁，唔知係全國定一個地區呢&hellip;"},{"pid":"216a7b5ad25df8e1d07e7167fe8f5d71eb8f9d8a","tid":2047000,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"但個Amy真係口震震聽落真係好驚"},{"pid":"337a71d5816f093ab98e156334c2bdb714d40ac0","tid":2047000,"uid":132859,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T21:01:01.000Z","msg":"咁啲looters同班racists有咩分別？<br />\n大家都冇守social contract<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26dcdf8aef64570c1d7ae3d56fa19080023025d","tid":2047000,"uid":301795,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T21:08:22.000Z","msg":"順帶一提，親身經歷，同美國人講美國仲有白警佢反應就好似我同你講香港有白警咁，難聽過粗口。雖然佢地警察會為咗哀悼死者而跪，但係明顯有部份美國人都係唔收貨。佢地嘅問題亦唔止係警暴，仲有個制度。尼點同香港其實真係有啲似。"},{"pid":"547f5607f6de0142968b0e7945e85351e7a878cb","tid":2047000,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T21:08:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"304dc20aa7ffcec2920599b7d619d5e90ac27be3","tid":2047000,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T21:10:39.000Z","msg":"佢地抗爭Ok，後期比共產國際搞臭左件事"},{"pid":"7326e52ca336dd532d9f6161edd9612319bb7a96","tid":2047000,"uid":145847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T21:10:48.000Z","msg":"講咁多去justify<br />\n客觀事實係有nigga 去劫neighbours 間舖去打路過呀婆打無辜白人，唔講唔知以為佢哋玩黑人至上主義清洗白人"},{"pid":"e17c77c0f7ffd6d248e9e810bc390c8f67ddbdde","tid":2047000,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T21:12:28.000Z","msg":"咁唔鍾意why not 返非洲？"},{"pid":"cc686ae408318ef0f12b32ca204aa78a1cd4d66d","tid":20470